MPic
====

MPic is an utility for making pictures in minecraft maps.

Dependencies
============

SDL2
SDL2_image

Usage
=====

mpic [picture]

Default file is "picture.jpg" if picture argument is omitted

Interface:
	- LMB: move frame
	- RMB: scale frame

	- [: decrease dithering
	- ]: increase dithering

	- r/R: amplify/reduce red channel
	- g/G amplify/reduce green channel
	- b/B: amplify/reduce blue channel

	- Backspace: reset
	- Enter: export
